    TEMPLATE: Blank Area Example

    This is a template for creating new feature areas.
    Copy this entire folder and rename to create a new area.

    Steps to create a new area:
    1. Copy Areas/Example to Areas/YourFeature
    2. Update the namespace in this file and _Imports.razor
    3. Update the @page route
    4. Add menu item in Program.cs RegisterDefaultMenuItems()
    5. Optionally add a feature flag in appsettings.json
*@

